Missile Combat
==================

Instructions 


	1- Start the game: 

	Just double click on the built jar file. The game would start automatically. 



	2- How to play: 

	The input device is the mouse. 
	To play you need to point with the mouse where to launch a missile and click the left or right button to release a missile. 


	3- Game over:

	When the user has no bases left.





